data.title: Je T'aime Moi Non Plus
data.text:
1976, 89 min. Directed by Serge Gainsbourg. Starring Jane Birkin, Joe Dallesandro and Hugues Quester.

Lates: New 4K restoration of Gainsbourg's directorial debut about a love triangle between a waitress (Birkin) and two gay truckers (Dallesandro and Quester). Gainsbourg wrote and recorded an eponymous song in 1967 for his girlfriend at the time, Brigitte Bardot.

6406 N. I-35 Ste. 3100, 512/322-0145
